
Directory Structure
===================

    topics/
        article-name/ //url version
            metadata.json 
            article //file with the real article
            assets/
                ...
        ...

Metadata Format
===============

    {
        "title":"What is npm?",
        "data-last-modified": "Today",
        "description": "A simple little article explaining the basic uses of npm",
        "tags": ["npm", "modules"],
        "difficulty": 1
    }

